      "text": "Redis (ioredis)\nGeo-Indexed Real-Time Tracking\n\nGEOADD / GEORADIUS queries\nBus position hashes (5-min TTL)\nRoute → Active Trips sets\nLocation event buffering\n\nGraceful degradation if unavailable",
